# ──────────────── 사전 준비: 로그인 (ADMIN_MASTER 계정) ────────────────

### 로그인 (Access Token 획득)
POST {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId" : "vhkdrb521",
  "password" : "ghkddlsrb1!"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}



### 전체 역할 목록 조회
GET {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/admin/authorization/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 역할 상세 조회 (연결된 권한 포함)
GET {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/admin/authorization/roles/a0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 전체 권한 목록 조회
GET {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/admin/authorization/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 역할별 권한 조회
GET {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/admin/authorization/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 역할에 권한 할당
POST {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/admin/authorization/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permissionName" : "READ"
}

### 역할에서 권한 해제
DELETE {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/admin/authorization/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions/READ
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 회원 역할/권한 조회
GET {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/admin/authorization/members/{{memberId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 회원 역할 변경
PUT {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/admin/authorization/members/{{memberId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleName" : "ADMIN_USER"
}
